Overview

This dashboard shows Vulnerability overview related to the Wiz Integration.

This dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the detection of ingested vulnerabilities.

It provides information about vulnerability and vulnerability assets. It also displays the distribution of vulnerabilities according to detection method and status. It also contains details regarding count of vulnerabilities over time.
